text: Eunidia nigroapicalis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Pic in 1925. It is known from Sumatra and Borneo.BioLib.cz - Eunidia nigroapicalis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1925
title: Eunidia nigroapicalis
